<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>第二十届运动会开幕式</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812227760.png" alt="1761812227760.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812227760.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">当金色的阳光洒满校园，当激昂的旋律响彻操场，属于我们的运动盛宴正式拉开帷幕！江西软件大学第二十届运动会如约而至，这不仅是一场速度与力量的角逐，更是一次青春与梦想的碰撞。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">此次开幕式在经济管理学院活力满满的啦啦操《幸运一击》中热力开场！灵动舞姿搭配欢快节奏，瞬间点燃现场氛围，用青春活力为运动会拉开完美序幕。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>PART.01</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>入场式：创意满格，活力出圈</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812250901.png" alt="1761812250901.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812250901.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812280701.png" alt="1761812280701.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812280701.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">入场仪式环节，国旗、校旗、会旗依次入场，庄严前行，昂首阔步。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812298344.png" alt="1761812298344.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812298344.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812317869.png" alt="1761812317869.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812317869.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812335586.png" alt="1761812335586.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812335586.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">随后，经管学院代表队身着特色服装，迈着整齐步伐走过主席台，他们喊着整齐的口号：经管经管，所向披靡；挑战极限，共创极限。同学们精神抖擞，面带笑容，活力四射，展现出经管学子的蓬勃朝气。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812359145.png" alt="1761812359145.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812359145.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812390689.png" alt="1761812390689.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812390689.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812412493.png" alt="1761812412493.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812412493.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812430235.png" alt="1761812430235.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812430235.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812446492.png" alt="1761812446492.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812446492.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812462876.png" alt="1761812462876.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812462876.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812500246.png" alt="1761812500246.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812500246.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>PART.02</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><strong>庄严升旗</strong></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">升国旗，奏国歌。全体师生面向国旗肃立齐唱《义勇军进行曲》，歌声嘹亮，唱出了对祖国的深深热爱和崇高敬意。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812532706.png" alt="1761812532706.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812532706.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812552886.png" alt="1761812552886.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812552886.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>PART.03</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">校领导致辞</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">执行校长范红铭为开幕式致开幕词。他首先向运动会的顺利召开表示祝贺，向筹备人员、裁判员及全体运动员致以感谢，并鼓励同学们以运动会为契机，发扬“更高、更快、更强”的体育精神，在赛场上挥洒汗水、超越自我，展现江软学子的青春担当。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812606871.png" alt="1761812606871.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812606871.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>PART.04</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">裁判员代表、运动员代表，宣誓</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">桂盼萍老师代表全体裁判员向大会庄严承诺，将秉持公平、公正、公开原则，认真履行裁判职责，保障比赛顺利进行。运动员代表郭建涛郑重宣誓，将严格遵守比赛规则，尊重对手、尊重裁判，全力以赴、赛出水平、赛出风格！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812625642.png" alt="1761812625642.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812625642.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812647804.png" alt="1761812647804.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812647804.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>PART.05</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>运动会开幕</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">“我宣布，江西软件大学第二十届运动会正式开始！”随着党委书记、督导专员饶勇的话音落下，现场掌声雷动、欢呼声此起彼伏。运动会正式进入精彩赛程，开幕式圆满落幕。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812670447.png" alt="1761812670447.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812670447.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812692530.png" alt="1761812692530.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812692530.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>PART.06</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>大型文体表演</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">开幕式后，还有文体表演精彩接档，昂扬的气韵扑面而来，将体育的热血与艺术的鲜活巧妙结融合，为这场体育盛会增添了更多青春活力与艺术色彩。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812724912.png" alt="1761812724912.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812724912.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812778038.png" alt="1761812778038.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812778038.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812801514.png" alt="1761812801514.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812801514.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812821886.png" alt="1761812821886.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812821886.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">开幕式的落幕，是赛场拼搏的开始。接下来让我们聚焦每一个精彩瞬间，为运动健儿们加油呐喊，共同见证他们在赛场上书写的热血青春！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812893370.png" alt="1761812893370.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761812893370.png" style="width: 50%;"></p>